      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It is in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
