    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission exhibits crisp engagement with no synchro wear. Mechanically, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014eliminating the common failure points of this chassis. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with fresh bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. The exterior finish is flawless, showing deep luster with zero oxidative degradation, while the interior preserves the factory Nappa leather bolster integrity. A truly turn-key specimen for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
