    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish with a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint look wet to the touch\u2014not a single stone chip or swirl mark to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather still retains its original scent, and every surface is free of wear or blemishes. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a complete, documented service history from the main dealer and recently fitted performance tires. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
